<br>
The people in that thread has soloed a lot of dangerous mobs, including mobs that are very-very tough and they were also likely a bit lucky.<br>
<br>
One standard group of lv 60 people (warrior, cleric, enchanter + 3 damage dealers) if they know what they do should be able to take down Vox without a problem. In all likelihood they don't even have to be lv 60 all of them.<br>
<br>
It isn't the 32khp that is the problem or the fearing or the despelling. The summoning is dangerous but survivable. When people are whiping killing Vox it is usually due to one of two things: She gets walled, CH's and kills everybody or she doesn't get interupted, CH's and kills everybody. I am having great trubble in seeing how a magician solo would handle the CH.<br>
<br>
Naggy on the other hand is a different beast, because he doesn't CH. It would still be a tough fight, but not entirely impossible.<br>
